*ffi-0.5.4 (31 Jan 2010)

  31 Jan 2010; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> +ffi-0.5.4.ebuild,
  +files/ffi-0.5.4-rakefile.patch, +metadata.xml:
